\DOC mk_pabs

\TYPE {mk_pabs : {{varstruct :term, body :term}} -> term}

\SYNOPSIS
Constructs a paired abstraction.

\DESCRIBE
{mk_pabs {{varstruct = --`(v1,..(..)..,vn)`--, body = t}}} returns the 
abstraction {--`\(v1,..(..)..,vn). t`--}. 

\FAILURE
Fails unless {varstruct} is an arbitrarily nested pair composed from variables.

\SEEALSO
dest_pabs, is_pabs, mk_abs.

\ENDDOC
